==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Interpale
<hw>In`ter*pale"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
place pales between or among; to separate by pales.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To interweave or interlace.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>Brende.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interparietal</ent>⟦br⟧
